column2: SELECT TOP # p.oiii_#_reqw_err as oir, p.h_beta_reqw_err as hbr, p.nii_#_reqw_err as nir, p.h_alpha_reqw_err as har, p.specObjID    FROM galSpecLine as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.specObjID = zns.specObjID    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.specObjID WHERE zns.nvote >= # and zns.p_cw > #
